     H            Y.
     F** EDTR06B ***************************************
     F*  EDIT LOCATION WITH HYPHEN                     *
     F*  J.WATANABE    2021.11.29                      *
     F*------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'EDTR06B'
     F*                    PARM           $LOC6   6
     F*                    PARM           $LOC9   9
     F*  IN  $LOC6 :  6A LOCATION 6 DIGITS
     F*  OUT $LOC9 :  1A LOCATION WITH HIPHEN
     F*-----------------------------------------
     F*  EX.  123456 --> 1-23-45-6
     F**************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 WLOC
     I                                        1   1 WLOC1
     I                                        2   3 WLOC2
     I                                        4   5 WLOC3
     I                                        6   6 WLOC4
     I            DS
     I                                        1   9 @LOC
     I                                        1   1 @LOC1
     I                                        2   2 HP1
     I                                        3   4 @LOC2
     I                                        5   5 HP2
     I                                        6   7 @LOC3
     I                                        8   8 HP3
     I                                        9  10 @LOC4
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $LOC6   6
     C                     PARM           $LOC9   9
      *
     C                     MOVEL$LOC6     WLOC
      *
     C                     MOVELWLOC1     @LOC1
     C                     MOVELWLOC2     @LOC2
     C                     MOVELWLOC3     @LOC3
     C                     MOVELWLOC4     @LOC4
      *
     C                     MOVE '-'       HP1
     C                     MOVE '-'       HP2
     C                     MOVE '-'       HP3
      *
     C                     MOVEL@LOC      $LOC9
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
